CommandScheduler
          A command scheduler will accept Commands and execute the at the time specified by a Schedule
Schedule
          A command in the CommandScheduler will run commands according to info provided in an instance of Schedule This version is only an wrapper to a Date, meaning that a command scheduled with this schedule object will only run once in that date
